<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'Privacy Policy' }) %>
<div class="app">
  <div class="main" style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 24px;">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 8px;">How we handle your data on the Dunky AI agent platform.</p>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 12px; margin-top: 4px;">Last updated: March 16, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card card-compact">
      <h3>What We Collect</h3>
      <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 20px; margin: 8px 0 0;">
        <li>Account email address (used for login and billing)</li>
        <li>Chat messages between you and your agent — stored in your private database</li>
        <li>Integration credentials (Slack OAuth tokens, Google OAuth tokens, Airtable tokens, etc.) — stored encrypted at rest</li>
        <li>Scheduled job configurations you create</li>
        <li>Basic server logs (request timestamps, error traces) for debugging — no message content is logged</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card card-compact">
      <h3>How We Use Your Data</h3>
      <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 20px; margin: 8px 0 0;">
        <li>To operate your hosted AI agent and connect it to the services you configure</li>
        <li>To forward your messages to the LLM provider for processing</li>
        <li>To process payments through Stripe</li>
        <li>To send you service-related emails (account setup, billing issues)</li>
        <li>We do not sell, rent, or share your data with third parties for marketing purposes</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card card-compact">
      <h3>Third-Party Services</h3>
      <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 20px; margin: 8px 0 0;">
        <li>LLM providers (Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, Groq) — your messages are sent to the provider for AI processing. Their privacy policies govern how they handle that data.</li>
        <li>Stripe — processes subscription payments. We do not store your credit card details.</li>
        <li>Slack, Gmail, Google Calendar, Notion, Airtable, Buffer, Luma, Twitter/X, Granola, ContactOut — only connected if you explicitly enable them. Credentials are encrypted and used solely to operate the integration you configured.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card card-compact">
      <h3>Data Storage & Security</h3>
      <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 20px; margin: 8px 0 0;">
        <li>Each agent runs in its own isolated Docker container with a dedicated database</li>
        <li>All sensitive credentials (OAuth tokens, API keys) are encrypted at rest using AES-256-GCM</li>
        <li>Dashboard access is protected by magic link authentication and session tokens</li>
        <li>TLS encryption in transit for all connections</li>
        <li>We do not have access to your decrypted credentials or chat history during normal operations</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card card-compact">
      <h3>Data Retention & Deletion</h3>
      <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 20px; margin: 8px 0 0;">
        <li>You can disconnect any integration at any time from your dashboard — this removes stored credentials</li>
        <li>Chat history is stored in your container's database and persists until you delete it or cancel your account</li>
        <li>If you cancel your subscription, your container and all associated data (database, credentials, chat logs) are permanently deleted</li>
        <li>You can request a full data export or deletion by contacting us</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card card-compact">
      <h3>Cookies</h3>
      <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 20px; margin: 8px 0 0;">
        <li>We use a single session cookie for dashboard authentication</li>
        <li>No tracking cookies, analytics scripts, or third-party cookies are used</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card card-compact">
      <h3>Contact</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
        If you have questions about this privacy policy or want to request data deletion, email us at
        <a href="mailto:dunkythehippocorn@gmail.com" style="color: var(--accent);">dunkythehippocorn@gmail.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 24px;">
      <a href="/" style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;">&larr; Back</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<%- include('partials/foot') %>
